# LoRa MQTT Bridge Application

## Purpose

Bridge MQTT messages from a local broker to several remote MQTT brokers for LoRaWAN gateways.

## Local Broker Topics

### Subscriptions (from LNS)
- `lora/+/+/up` - Uplink messages (lora format)
- `scada/+/up` - Uplink messages (scada format)
- `lora/+/+/moved` - Device moved notifications
- `lora/+/joined` - Device join notifications

### Publications (to LNS)
- `lora/%s/down` - Downlink messages (lora format, %s = deveui)
- `scada/%s/down` - Downlink messages (scada format, %s = deveui)
- `lora/%s/clear` - Clear queue messages

## Configuration Options

- Select between `lora/+/+/up` or `scada/+/up` for uplinks
- Select between `lora/%s/down` or `scada/%s/down` for downlinks
- Filter fields in uplink messages
- Filter uplinks to each remote broker based on DevEUI, JoinEUI, or AppEUI

